    "quote": "I'd heard a rumor, Autumn," started Winston, meeting her outside her reptile enclosure, "Heard that Donald found out you were back to your old tricks." ... "Imagine his surprise," continued Winston, "down in the bunker alone, knowing his old friend is involved in illegal matters again."",
